content:
I apologize for my mistake. Here are a few more suggestions for possible words that "Gary Niami" could be an anagram of:

1. "Grainy"
2. "Rangy"
3. "Maniag"
4. "Imag" (a shortened version of "imaging")

I hope one of these suggestions is the word you had in mind. If not, please provide more information and I will do my best to help.
